		<title>台塑石化不只為航空加油　也為職棒加油!!</title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/08/23/%e5%8f%b0%e5%a1%91%e7%9f%b3%e5%8c%96%e4%b8%8d%e5%8f%aa%e7%82%ba%e8%88%aa%e7%a9%ba%e5%8a%a0%e6%b2%b9%e3%80%80%e4%b9%9f%e7%82%ba%e8%81%b7%e6%a3%92%e5%8a%a0%e6%b2%b9/</link>
		
